title: Innovate Maryland: Emerging Tech + Art Expo | MAVRIC - UMD
content: Innovate Maryland: Emerging Tech + Art Expo | MAVRIC  UMD
description: Join the University of Maryland Campus Community on Tuesday, May 10th from 5-9:00 PM for a fun evening exploring and interacting with emerging technologies through immersive media art, interactive augmented experiences, and virtual adventures in the Discovery District.
